sequenceDiagram
    participant Sender as 发送者
    participant Consumer as ChatMessageConsumer
    participant MySQL as MySQL message表
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant SSE as SseEmitterManager
    participant FE as 接收者前端(AppShell)

    Sender->>Consumer: 聊天消息消费
    Consumer->>MySQL: INSERT message(type=chat)
    Consumer->>Redis: INCR message:unread:{receiverId}
    Consumer->>SSE: sendToUser(receiverId, "message", data)
    SSE->>FE: SSE 事件推送
    FE->>FE: unreadCount++ (红点+1)
    FE->>FE: ElNotification 弹窗("新消息: 你好")
